            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#zayadine1986"><p>Was beautified and paved with mosaics this hall of the venerable 
                Blues in the time of the first year of the office of Constantine and Stephan the logoteutes in the year 640, 
                in the month of Audnaios, in the 11th indiction. (January 578)</p>
           </div>
           <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
           <p>This place of the most honourable Blues was adorned and given mosaic decoration when Konstantinos was exarch for the first time and 
               Stephanos was logeutes, in the year 640, month Audnaios, year 11 of the indiction.</p>
                
         </div>
